msgid "AVIF WebP Image Converter"
msgstr "AVIF WebP图像转换器"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:65
msgid "Features"
msgstr "功能"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:66
msgid ""
"This plug-in will convert all images upload to media library to AVIF or WebP "
"format depending on your PHP situation. Preferentially it uses Imagick to "
"convert uploaded images to AVIF format. If the server does not support, it "
"will try to convert images to AVIF with GD, if not support, it will try to "
"convert images to WebP with Imagick, lastly try to convert images to WebP "
"with GD. If none of them are supported, the original image will be uploaded. "
"If the uploaded image format is AVIF or WebP, no conversion will be "
"performed."
msgstr ""
"本插件将根据你的PHP状况将所有上传的图片转换为AVIF或WebP格式，优先采用Imagick"
"将图像转换为AVIF格式，如果服务器不支持，依次尝试GD转换图像为AVIF，Imagick转换"
"图像为WebP，GD转换图像为WebP。如果都不支持，则原图上传。如果上传的图片为AVIF"
"或WebP，则不进行转换。"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:71 includes/avif-webp-converter.php:89
msgid "Installed"
msgstr "已安装"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:75 includes/avif-webp-converter.php:93
msgid "AVIF support"
msgstr "AVIF支持"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:79 includes/avif-webp-converter.php:97
msgid "WebP support"
msgstr "WebP支持"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:103
msgid "Conversion policy"
msgstr "转格式策略"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:107
msgid "Current policy"
msgstr "目前策略"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:110
msgid "to avif by Imagick"
msgstr "使用Imagick转avif"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:112
msgid "to avif by GD"
msgstr "使用GD转avif"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:114
msgid "to WebP by Imagick"
msgstr "使用Imagick转WebP"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:116
msgid "to WebP by GD"
msgstr "使用GD转WebP"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:123
msgid "More to read"
msgstr "阅读更多"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:124
msgid ""
"Both AVIF and WebP are modern image formats designed to reduce file sizes "
"while maintaining quality. AVIF is newer and offers more efficient "
"compression, often resulting in smaller file sizes than WebP. It means you "
"can get faster download speed at the same image quality for images on web "
"page by using AVIF images."
msgstr ""
"AVIF 和 WebP 都是现代图像格式，旨在在保持质量的同时减小文件大小。AVIF 格式较"
"新，压缩效率更高，通常比 WebP 格式的文件大小更小。这意味着使用 AVIF 格式，网"
"页上的图像在保持相同画质的情况下，可以获得更快的加载速度。"

#: includes/avif-webp-converter.php:125
msgid ""
"Imagick and GD are both PHP extension, they both capable of converting "
"traditional image format to AVIF or WebP on latest versions. Imagick is not "
"limited by PHP memory, and the converted image quality is better than GD, "
"but it usually needs to be installed separately, and the converted image "
"size is slightly larger than GD. GD is more popular, and the conversion "
"speed is faster than Imagick, the result image size is slightly smaller, but "
"the result image quality is usually slightly worse than Imagick."
msgstr ""
"Imagick和GD都是PHP扩展，最新版都可以将传统图像格式转换为AVIF或WebP格式。"
"Imagick不受PHP内存设置限制，转换后的图像质量优于GD，但通常需要单独安装，且转"
"换后的图像尺寸略大于 GD。GD普及度较广，转换速度比Imagick略快，转换后的图像尺"
"寸略小，但转换后的图像质量通常略差于Imagick。"

